Package com.solana.digitalassetlinks

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    AssetLinksJSONParser.StatementMatcherCallback
    A callback to be invoked when a StatementMatcher match occurs
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    AndroidAppPackageVerifier
    Verifier for Android app packages using Digital Asset Links
    AssetLinksGrammar
    The defined grammar for Digital Asset Links
    AssetLinksJSONParser
    A Digital Asset Links JSON parser
    StatementMatcher
    A StatementMatcher is used to test a set of conditions against a Digital Asset Links statement
    StatementMatcher.Builder
    Implements the Builder pattern for StatementMatcher
    URISourceVerifier  
    URISourceVerifier.StatementMatcherWithCallback
    A data class wrapper to bind a StatementMatcher and a AssetLinksJSONParser.StatementMatcherCallback together, for matching against an Asset Links tree.
  • Exception Summary 
    Exception Description
    AndroidAppPackageVerifier.CouldNotVerifyPackageException
    This exception indicates that the verification process could not be completed (for e.g., due to a network error).
    AssetLinksJSONParser.AssetLinksJSONParserException
    The base type for all AssetLinksJSONParser exceptions
    AssetLinksJSONParser.IllFormattedStatementException
    Thrown when the Asset Links JSON is not well-formed
    AssetLinksJSONParser.MatcherException
    Thrown when a matcher generates an Exception during processing
    AssetLinksJSONParser.TooManyIncludesException
    Thrown when the number of includes in the Asset Links tree exceeds the allowed limit
    URISourceVerifier.CouldNotVerifyException
    Indicates that the Asset Links tree could not be verified for any reason
